Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:47.58,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So it was your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.36,0:01:49.59,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.89,0:01:51.43,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.74,0:01:52.34,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:53.62,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get cheeky now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:59.30,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,It's everyone's problem; \Nnot just yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.61,0:02:02.00,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Know your own limits, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.41,0:02:03.60,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.61,0:02:07.01,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.58,0:02:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 12\NSee ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:26.43,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Can't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:31.57,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Same goes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.57,0:02:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to get rest on a chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:36.35,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You can take my spot on the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:39.34,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but that'll leave you \Nin there with Minchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:42.19,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think she'll mind that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:42.88,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:44.43,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:45.97,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:48.90,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I can rest easier on this couch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:03:00.28,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru, do you... have a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.81,0:03:02.02,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:05.57,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not at the moment, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.54,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Figured as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:12.52,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You don't handle women very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:15.63,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But I think you're very kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:18.92,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I think you need to \Nbelieve yourself and to fest it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:19.85,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Fest-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.52,0:03:29.59,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were depressed \Nabout your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:31.34,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,The real cause is your \Nboyfriend in Tokyo, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:34.08,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:37.21,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I had made the right decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he would have been my \Nboyfriend now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:40.39,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:42.36,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,So I was right, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:44.99,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,No you weren't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you believe me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:50.80,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,You talk a damn lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but your face also shows \Nwhat you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:55.75,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm off to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:56.71,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.55,0:04:13.35,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to kidnap Satsuki Matsumae.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:14.85,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,What?\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.07,0:04:18.38,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Satsuki Matsumae has no intention \Nto visit the Kissuiso.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:21.21,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, I will force her to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:22.61,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:24.11,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:28.45,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,This is her place of occupation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:30.65,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Taking account her path \Nto work from the station,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.65,0:04:32.22,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,it would be most wise to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ambush her in this back \Nalley and kidnap her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:36.68,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a car, and \Nthere are three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:38.54,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,We should be able to win
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,against her monstrous strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:41.59,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:44.05,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,What do we think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:44.97,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:48.37,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:50.12,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but it comes with one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:54.32,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,We're taking this Koichi \Nguy along as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:55.73,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:57.29,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:05:00.54,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,That's the condition to have \Nmy help in the kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:02.39,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:03.57,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Minko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:08.25,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do some Tokyo sightseeing \Nuntil Ohana brings Koichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.59,0:05:10.94,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,But the breakfast...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:12.54,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eat any more of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:15.29,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,You'll gain nothing from eating \Ncheap toast like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:18.82,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo has many famous places to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:21.29,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,It's also important to visit places \Nas a customer to train your tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:23.03,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:33.22,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The number you have dialed \Nis not in service or- {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Dialing: Ko
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:39.98,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He must be mad at what \NI did yesterday... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:43.43,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm supposed to take him along? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:46.31,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't even know how to face him. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:50.80,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But then again, there's no way \NI can kidnap Mom alone... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:54.83,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, what does Ko have \Nanything to do with this? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:56.92,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that I think about it... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:58.52,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't even *have* \Nto think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:05:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:09.84,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get in touch with him via phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I also went to his work \Nto see if he was around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:14.43,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I did everything I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.61,0:06:17.81,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.71,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I did what I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru will forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:24.29,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You're... Ohana, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:27.53,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:32.88,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have feelings for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let him go already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:36.04,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Let him go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:38.41,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:42.04,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me sound like a villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:44.99,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:47.72,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I *was* trying to \Nkidnap him, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:49.72,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking to yourself for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.48,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That's creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:52.72,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:55.72,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,When I say "let him \Ngo," I mean his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:07:00.70,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, this bench is where
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked Koichi out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:05.07,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:06.96,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,On that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:09.45,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:12.55,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:15.87,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going out with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:18.84,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,No, she's deferring her \Nanswer to a later time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:21.58,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?! That's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:25.50,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, maybe that's not her intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:29.13,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm waiting for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:30.05,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:30.96,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:34.25,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to waiting, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:41.26,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid of her safety if \NI'm not watching over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:47.19,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:49.78,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You've made a nest on his feelings \Nand you're resting on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:52.66,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I-I do like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:54.91,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I do like Ko, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:56.23,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,And then you're going \Nto say something like,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:08:00.20,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,"I don't like him as a boy. I \Nlike him as a human being."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.66,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:04.17,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Then how do you like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.34,0:08:06.21,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:08.90,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,As a hu-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:11.14,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,As a living creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:12.21,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:20.93,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.57,0:08:23.52,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:26.16,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,N-Noth-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:28.09,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Igarashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:30.72,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Your break's already up, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:33.86,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:36.77,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Please make the decision yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:41.41,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,If you continue to step all \Nover his kindness like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.57,0:08:44.67,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:53.61,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going straight for a little \Nwhile and make a right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.61,0:08:54.32,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:59.24,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,It's... like a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:04.70,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:06.23,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Gladly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:10.74,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:12.23,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.83,0:09:17.97,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave a single grain of rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:23.37,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,That broiled fish was half raw,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,allowing us to enjoy the \Ndifferences in texture.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:29.44,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,But taking into account the residual \Nheat and the time it was served...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:30.15,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel too good...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:31.13,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Throw up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:32.21,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,If you need to throw \Nup to eat more, do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:34.92,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't come to Tokyo for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:37.92,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,We need to learn the tastes \Nof the famous stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:41.99,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana's case comes after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:50.50,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The town Ko lives in, which is \Nthe town I used to live in. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:54.49,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The dramaless town which I despised. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:10:00.24,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She... was a nice girl. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:06.25,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's able to face her opponent \Nclearly and seriously. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:10.17,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But doesn't living in a hot \Nspring inn sound dramatic?{K: From ep1} {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:14.79,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If there was a drama \Nwith us starring in it, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:18.43,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd probably be the antagonist. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ko
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:29.63,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The doors are closing. \NPlease watch your step. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:31.56,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:32.92,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:35.60,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry, it looks like \NI missed a few calls. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:36.48,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was napping. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:38.84,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:40.07,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:42.27,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The girl at work gave me a call. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:43.45,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.98,0:10:46.34,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,You came to the bookstore, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:48.73,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Y-Yeah. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.73,0:10:52.46,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I mean, no, I just kinda dropped by. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.33,0:10:58.13,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You remind me of how I used to be. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:00.34,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:03.24,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,I actually went to your place
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I was on break from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:06.59,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,My place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:08.58,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you were going to the wedding hall {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to look for whats-his-face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.67,0:11:20.29,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanted to pay the Kissuiso a visit, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:23.27,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but you seemed really busy. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.27,0:11:25.35,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:27.89,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, Ohana? You listening? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:32.03,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the antagonist for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.03,0:11:32.81,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:38.97,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, I need to take \Nmy mom to Kissuiso,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.97,0:11:42.13,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,and in order to do that, \NI need to take you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:42.87,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:45.02,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not making any sense. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:47.61,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why I called you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:51.54,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You helped me back then too,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:55.40,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,but I seeked help from you again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:58.91,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I tell myself that I need to \Nwork hard and to fest it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but in the end, I'm only \Nthinking about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:04.61,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wasn't thinking about the people {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who are looking over \Nme and cheering for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:10.80,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I've been terrible to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:13.19,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:19.96,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get what \Nyou're saying, but... sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:21.25,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:23.23,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:24.56,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:25.75,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}See ya. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:38.44,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Ko tried to look over someone \Nawful like me forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:41.49,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Even then, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:43.34,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:49.02,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I said "later," but he \Nresponded with "see ya."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:53.00,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean there \Nwon't be a next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:57.92,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.43,0:13:00.75,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the one who \Nwants to cry the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:03.76,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:18.73,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Bonboris...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:25.77,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I threw up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:27.18,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:28.92,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Time for sushi then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:30.29,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:42.26,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to eating sushi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:43.79,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:47.63,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, what should I get next?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:55.11,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Does the fact that Ohana is out {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.11,0:13:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with another guy bother you that much?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:03.69,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I haven't even been \Naway for half a year, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:05.94,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but it all feels so nostalgic. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:08.02,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The town I hate. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:11.80,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I always liked it \Naround this time of day. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:14.16,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The lights that look like bonboris {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}appear as though they \Nlead to the future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.97,0:14:18.75,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not the only one. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:21.04,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone has bonboris. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even Ko.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:26.57,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I'm sure Mom has one too. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:30.41,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hurt Ko. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:34.16,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ko was festing it up for me. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:37.33,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was hurt by Mom. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:41.20,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'm sure mom was festing it up too. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:43.15,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone is treading their {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}paths with their own thoughts in mind, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}trying to sparkle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:49.26,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:52.08,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get it this time for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:14:55.38,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, slowly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:57.35,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I need to grab the tag on the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:14:58.51,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to ask him. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:15:00.75,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After he gets that, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to ask him about his feelings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Missing line
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}missingline{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}missing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,missing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,missing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:18.23,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Minchi? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:20.19,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana! How was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:23.47,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, about that Koichi guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.76,0:15:24.65,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:25.46,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:26.19,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,You gave up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:29.19,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take Ko with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I wasn't thinking about \Nmy mom's feelings either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.20,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:36.80,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:41.09,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What about your luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:42.21,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,It's over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:45.71,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. You can open up a shop with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:48.05,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,They're souvenirs for the \Nfolks back at the inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:53.35,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm... sorry I decided \Neverything on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:54.80,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading to your mom's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:56.68,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:15:58.74,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we're not \Nkidnapping her anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agreed with it at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:04.19,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to rest \Nuntil I yell at her
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about her article.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:12.45,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, I was going to try \Nand fest it up on my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.46,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.46,0:16:18.53,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll lead the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.79,0:16:33.34,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... she should be in that building.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:36.85,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:39.53,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,You're late today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.59,0:16:44.40,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:45.47,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:47.67,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,Are those people from the Kissuiso?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:50.86,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, how lucky am I to \Nhave people pick me up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:55.00,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,You told me you were going \Nto take me there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:56.98,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to take a few days off,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I was thinking about \Ngoing to a hot springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:17:00.87,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:09.38,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you have good taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:12.34,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,I can actually get you tickets \Nthrough my work, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:13.43,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:15.34,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:17.78,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You kept saying no when \NI asked you to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:18.92,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.92,0:17:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to take a few days off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:23.56,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,The Yunosagi area is a good \Nplace to go to avoid the heat,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:25.98,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,but... what's the name \Nof that new hotel again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:27.67,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,The Yunosagi Silas?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:28.31,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:30.45,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,That place is too popular,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and there's no way I can stay \Nthere without a reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:36.10,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,The Kissuiso isn't like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:37.07,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:39.38,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you wrote
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.38,0:17:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the article because \NYunosagi Silas paid you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:43.84,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, who cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.84,0:17:45.11,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,We care!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:48.26,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you going to say \Nsomething to her, Tohru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:48.84,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:52.09,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since she's coming \Nto the Kissuiso,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:53.56,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,we can have a chat later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:55.22,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:58.04,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's chat over a few drinks, Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.54,0:18:03.19,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could it be that he likes older women? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:06.54,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could it be this family in general? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:07.10,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:11.28,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, did you meet Ko, Ohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:14.74,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Is Ko short for Koichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:15.53,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:17.43,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,Your boyfriend, right, Ohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:19.80,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:23.86,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I like this song, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.85,0:18:33.87,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Minchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:36.37,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:38.69,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Take this as a thank-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:39.85,Default,Minchi,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:40.39,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.92,0:18:42.64,Default,Minchi,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru was the one who worked hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:48.02,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,He's a lot nicer than I'd thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.18,0:18:51.29,Default,Minchi,0000,0000,0000,,I take that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:55.77,Default,Minchi,0000,0000,0000,,He worked hard, but not \Nas hard as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:03.41,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,Care for a smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:06.79,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a chef, so I choose not to smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.69,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,How diligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.28,0:19:13.09,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,So why did you decide to \Ncome all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:15.34,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:16.76,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:22.05,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,You're only a few years \Nolder than Ohana, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:24.28,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,You're very mature, Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.23,0:19:27.56,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:31.19,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana really went all out on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which reminded me of \Nsome things in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:38.00,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,I said the same things as a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:41.57,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.09,0:19:44.29,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're always so focused on work. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been holding back all this time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:50.83,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop fighting! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:20:00.87,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my mother's work is a \Nlot more honorable than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:03.79,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,How did you feel as you \Nwere writing the article?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.69,0:20:07.22,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,While writing to discredit \Nyour own home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:12.39,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't include a single \Nlie in the article.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:16.73,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,That inn really is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:19.40,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think you can write an \Narticle with just your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:21.53,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:25.11,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,But we're always trying new things!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:26.12,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:29.07,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you \Ndecorate the exterior,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.07,0:20:31.02,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,what's important is \Nwhat's on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.36,0:20:33.00,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,Having consideration for the customers
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and making sure they enjoy themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.10,0:20:37.75,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,She's got it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.76,0:20:42.43,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Mom's always right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:45.89,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,I think Ohana is a pretty \Nlucky girl, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.33,0:20:49.60,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,Having a Mom who isn't \Nright should be amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.09,0:20:51.34,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,What do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.34,0:20:52.35,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:57.23,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,We should probably get going soon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:20:58.41,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:05.11,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,But hear this. Ohana is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:07.27,Default,Satsu,0000,0000,0000,,The first thing she did
